    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鉴赏家评测</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/8e3fd46a5ab2faa55415cd0b6c6554e3.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=146 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/84b297df07fdb602fe694352e424d535.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=146 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/d16e8a0a1a54535d532103e2975f5b6c.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/6e6b90672eb6166b0006f8de36ef304e.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=146 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/1c414a2c1e292a1cb495c508676e5fc9.poster.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/1c414a2c1e292a1cb495c508676e5fc9.webm?t=1728346417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/1c414a2c1e292a1cb495c508676e5fc9.mp4?t=1728346417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >射击、摧毁、掠夺、继续！</h2><strong>我们熟知而喜爱的复古射击类街机游戏在VR平台上强势归来！</strong><br>夜星：联盟是一款以丰富的战斗、跌宕的故事和排行榜为核心的复古街机游戏！<br>驾驶上你的重型战列巡洋舰，网罗出一支足以抗衡重创了人类的A.I.的舰队。这个联盟将是引领人类脱离灭绝危险的唯一希望。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/6d1da86355aa9354ecad6919c03d6006.poster.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/6d1da86355aa9354ecad6919c03d6006.webm?t=1728346417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/6d1da86355aa9354ecad6919c03d6006.mp4?t=1728346417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>当你在美丽无垠的星系中奋勇作战时，银河战争的全景亦将围绕着你铺展开来。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>驾驶</strong>有着直观且灵敏的第三人称控制模式的夜星战列巡洋舰 <br></li><li> <strong>自定义</strong>你的军火库，我们有着花样繁多的嵌入式武器和多用途模块<br></li><li> <strong>打造</strong>一支舰队并调配他们的装备，作战舰队将会让你如虎添翼<br></li><li> <strong>发射</strong>多种多样的激光、爆能弹、高射炮以及核武器<br></li><li> <strong>摧毁</strong>无尽的至高首脑舰队群<br></li><li> <strong>装备</strong>进攻和防御护盾、维修单位、伤害和射速模块<br></li><li> <strong>继续</strong>在本地和线上排行榜当中作战并成为声名远扬的夜星指挥官<br></li><li> <strong>升级</strong>你的战列巡洋舰，加强舰体、模块插槽、装甲和火力！<br></li><li> <strong>发掘</strong>泰拉战役中存活下来的指挥官们的故事</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >泰拉之陨</h2>在建立联盟并在星系外缘寻找一片净土的同时发掘这些泰拉战役中存活下来的指挥官们的故事。然而逃脱计划被陡然打乱，塔莉博士也察觉到自己正被机械们玩弄在股掌之中！<br><br><br>营救这些充满传奇色彩的指挥官们，充分利用他们独特的力量和能力来帮助自己！只有这样你才有机会对抗来势汹汹的至高首脑。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/98c5ce65b203db71d77202157fef0ac0.poster.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/98c5ce65b203db71d77202157fef0ac0.webm?t=1728346417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >爆炸性的火力与多功能模块</h2>在立志灭绝人类的反乱AI手中拯救人类殖民地的同时寻找并解锁各式重型武器、防御设备乃至灭世装置！ <br><br><br>从自动相位爆能弹、高射火炮、大功率激光到热制导火箭舱和毁灭性的核武器 - 联盟将不惜一切代价抵达星系外缘！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/e4d1a9e36b437969b9dbf65816bc9624.poster.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/e4d1a9e36b437969b9dbf65816bc9624.webm?t=1728346417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/e4d1a9e36b437969b9dbf65816bc9624.mp4?t=1728346417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全球评测</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/d8a602edce4da757bf424568314ee5fd.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=146 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/864970/extras/6db01f7a82ff7574ad2403ca70e56b9f.avif?t=1728346417\" width=624 height=146 /></span><br><br><br>这是一款在VR平台上重新诠释街机射击体验的游戏。 <strong>射击、摧毁、掠夺、继续！</strong> 驾驶上你的重型战列巡洋舰，网罗出一支足以抗衡重创了人类的A.I.的舰队。这个联盟将是引领人类脱离灭绝危险的唯一希望。",
